AUDIO: 'Controlnet weights and loading and&nbsp; processing node for ANIMA Preview 3&nbsp;&nbsp; has been released very recently. The&nbsp; node is called "Controlnet LLLight".&nbsp;&nbsp; And today we are going to explore one of&nbsp; the controlnet weights for ANIMA Preview 3.&nbsp;&nbsp; Let\'s look at the repo first. As you can see here,&nbsp; the nodes are from the well-known dev Kohya-SS.&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[00:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
